Interested parties are invited to submit comments on these and other pertinent issues related to the need for a Federal
restriction that animal rabies vaccines be distributed and used only by or under the direct supervision of a licensed
veterinarian. Written comments should be submitted within the 90-day comment period specified in this notice under
the section entitled ``

DATES

'' to the person listed under the section entitled ``

ADDRESSES

''. All comments received on or before the close of the comment period will be considered in determining the appropriate
course of action.





