II. Background


A. Impetus for Change 


Housing agencies have been submitting to HUD data forms for each family assisted under the public housing, Indian
housing, and Section 8 Rental Certificate, Rental Voucher and Moderate Rehabilitation Programs. The Forms HUD-50058,
Family Report, and HUD-50058-FSS, Family Self-Sufficiency Addendum, concern family characteristics,
rent, income, subsidy payments and participation in the Family Self-Sufficiency Program. 

